&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Constrafor is a SaaS and fintech platform purpose-built for construction. We are setting new standards of productivity and cost-efficiency for the way General Contractors and Subcontractors manage procurement &amp;amp; financial transactions. With over $30 million of VC financing, we are forging the path for construction innovation. Join us on our mission to advance the largest industry in the world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a proactive and results-oriented Account Manager to join our team. The ideal person will be responsible for cultivating strong relationships with our existing subcontractor clients while helping expand the participation of our Early Pay Program. You will collaborate closely with sales, credit, and finance teams to streamline workflows, implement best practices, and maximize customer growth. The Account Manager will play a crucial role in supporting our customers and growing the overall portfolio.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
