&lt;li&gt;Grow customer participation and drive a healthy referral program.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and process client requests accurately and efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate strong, long-lasting relationships with SMB subcontractors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in resolving any issues or concerns raised by clients in a prompt and professional manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate clients on the benefits and features of the Early Pay Program, addressing any questions or concerns they may have.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams to ensure seamless ongoing support for our clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor client satisfaction and identify opportunities for expanding the usage of our EPP product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay informed about industry trends, regulatory changes, and competitive offerings to effectively position Constrafor&#39;s Early Pay Program in the market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
