&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and relationship-building skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Results-oriented mindset with a bias towards action&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to analyze client needs and tailor solutions to meet their specific requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated with a drive to exceed targets and deliver exceptional customer service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of financial concepts such as cash flow management or receivable financing is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
