&lt;li&gt;Strong financial modeling background.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working in a high-growth, fast-paced startup environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in construction finance, supply chain finance, or similar asset classes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
